{"tid":2488792,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚晚 咸魚雞粒豆腐煲","createTime":"2021-04-14T12:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T12:59:10.000Z","uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d19c5179b153d25f6d5e9cecb054350e83b36752","tid":2488792,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"勁好味仲要係黃店個例湯又足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQATjYK3AnQmfL3cUSuaPMFPxD9cirjkn18m2EwH9ZAm8?filename=RpqAH0m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpqAH0m.png&h=1429f62a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSWy6ESc8QDGfVfPFq2753nQ4M6AaYi9BM88CRXf4QUmE?filename=R6KawTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6KawTG.png&h=81029e6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f07d19a44eb68185d29e13d35533ca6d79a6b26","tid":2488792,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"LM咸魚雞粒潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28157eee7e829fd3fbb96ec410b1a330a7da4086","tid":2488792,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"早排係某間餐廳做PARTTIME廚房仔 <br />\n做左2日都算OK <br />\n點知上星期日實在多人食野 <br />\n搞到成個廚房忙到仆街 <br />\n但都唔算咩大問題 <br />\n直至有個侍應就入來 <br />\n我見佢面色慌張,心諗佢係咪做錯野呢? <br />\n點知佢大叫一聲&quot;咸魚雞粒豆腐煲一個!!!&quot; <br />\n成班廚房師傅同一時間停晒手用一種震驚既眼神望住個侍應仔 <br />\n我都呆晒,到低發生咩事呢 <br />\n只見大廚係褲袋中拿一支煙出來,慢慢地放係口中,再點著佢 <br />\n之後講左一句&quot;準備.......&quot; <br />\n到低煮咸魚雞粒豆腐煲要準備d咩呢? <br />\n突然之間成班廚房佬一齊除褲 <br />\n拿條鳩出來係到&quot;卒&quot;個龜頭!!!! <br />\n我心諗咩事? <br />\n點知大廚即係叫我一聲,你仲唔快d準備?知唔知個客等緊架?! <br />\n我只好跟住其他人一起咁樣做,但完全唔舍有咩意義 <br />\n只係卒下卒下,卒到d鳩屎出來,個大廚即係拿我d鳩屎放係個鼻到聞一聞<br />\n講左聲&quot;果然夠咸魚味.....&quot; <br />\n到個一下我終於明白了,原來一個靚的咸魚雞粒豆腐煲<br />\n係要靠鳩屎去吊出個種咸魚味....... <br />\n集合了數十人鳩屎,果然令樓主吃得津津有味"},{"pid":"6e481c4fa02e15c03b85f8acbea36b95296031ef","tid":2488792,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}